{"tid":419394,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"睇中醫趕造人 陳柏宇被老婆誤會腎虧","createTime":"2017-09-30T12:38:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T12:38:34.000Z","uid":14730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c546264993288a73d2faf4624968a81b224078e4","tid":419394,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T12:38:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/30/203819_c24f568249cd0c71e5236e3c1d14fef0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F30%2F203819_c24f568249cd0c71e5236e3c1d14fef0.jpg&h=8cb7b8ae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n陳柏宇（Jason）與太太符曉薇昨日出席化妝品活動，Jason為老婆塗唇膏兼送吻放閃。兩人剛搬新屋，實用面積800呎仍嫌未夠大，Jason爆老婆由化妝品到廚具也愛收藏，他們需要4萬呎的屋才夠用。符曉薇投訴老公愛清理屋企，不斷掉她的珍藏，坦言為此吵架，但總是和氣收場。為加快造人速度，兩人睇中醫調理身體，符曉薇搞笑聽錯醫師指Jason腎虧，原來是讚他腎功能好；他們希望早日有喜訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2xKjNdh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2xKjNdh&d=S4zWsKm%2BY%2Fb0UDJCxtvU4sn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=157e4aa9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2xKjNdh</a>"}]}